member.remarks:
Creates a new administrator with the provided registration details. Only users with Manager role are authorized to perform this action.
Sample request: POST /api/admin/newAdmin/create Authorization: Bearer {manager-token} Content-Type: application/json
{ "email": "admin@example.com", "password": "SecurePass123!", "firstName": "John", "lastName": "Doe", "phoneNumber": "12345678901", "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01" }

members.member:
Deposits amount of money to a specific account
Deposit request model Success message with account number
Sample request: POST /api/admin/account/deposit { "toAccount":"e19add5a-472c-46eb-be47-b3c40c691b62", "amount":0.00 }
/// Amount is deposited successfully to the account Invalid operation (e.g., account is inactive) User is not authenticated or authorized Account not found Internal server error

Deposits amount of money from customer's current account to a specific account
Transfer request model Success message with account number
Sample request: POST /api/customer/accounts/current/transfers { "toAccount":"e19add5a-472c-46eb-be47-b3c40c691b62", "amount":0.00 }
/// Amount is transferred successfully to the account Invalid operation (e.g.,one of the accounts is inactive) User is not authenticated or authorized Any of the accounts is not found Internal server error
